import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import Home from './pages/Home'

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <Switch>
      <Route exact path="/">
        <Home />
      </Route>
      <Route path="/Fiche-Logement">
        <Fiche />
      </Route>
    </Switch>
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)
